Cleasaiche ainmeil ameirigeanach, dh'fhas e cliuteach as deidh sreath de dh'fhiolmaichean miorbhaileach aig toiseach nan 70an, [[Dog Day Afternoon]], [[Serpico]], ach gu h-araidh [[The Godfather]], far an do chluich e [[Micheal Corleone]].  Chluich e Micheal da thrup eile anns [[The Godfather Part II]] agus [[The Godfather Part III]].

Ged tha cliu aige mar fear dhe na cleasaichean as fhearr a bha ann a-riamh, agus bha e air a mholadh sia tursan airson Duais an Acadamaidh, cha d' fhuair e greim air 'Oscar' gus 1991 airson [[Scent of a Woman]] far an do chluich e Seann Shaighdear Dhall.

As deidh Revolution ann an 1985, fiolm eiginneach mu dheidhinn Cogadh Neo-Eisimealachais nan Ameirgeanach, sguir e dheth fiolmaichean a dheanamh.  Ach thill e anns na 90an, far an do nochd e ann an sreth de dh'fhiolmaichean, 's ged nach robh iad cho math ris a' chuid a rinn a chliu san 70an, dhearbh iad aite Phacino mar chleasaiche chudtromach.  



